{"tid":544574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過冬天沖凍水涼?","createTime":"2018-01-29T16:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T12:06:12.000Z","uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"553f1e95376f3f682699af69765ac89b3c2dec3e","tid":544574,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"今日天氣溫度得返個位數，突然諗返起前幾年有幾日都係個位數溫度，凍到抽筋，點知個熱水爐因為太凍而著唔到，結果果幾日連續沖咗幾日凍水，凍到黐孖筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好彩捱得住過咗果幾日，如果唔係我而家應該唔會喺到同大家講到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家個熱水爐整返好，唔想再經歷返果種凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befe99f2a5005f67352cc3c714a4f9f6c3164b8e","tid":544574,"uid":91497,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"唔沖咪算，何必折磨自已，或者去體育館沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3e1b055c2884f88d8727540c372d19cc1a35b9","tid":544574,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"befe99f2a5005f67352cc3c714a4f9f6c3164b8e","tid":544574,"uid":91497,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"唔沖咪算，何必折磨自已，或者去體育館沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:04:59.000Z","msg":"可能自己有潔癖，每日at least要沖一次涼，唔沖唔舒服咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f8805f1c3c21c7aa51a250835f0c498b1cc292","tid":544574,"uid":128565,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"沖開液態氮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a517fb7b3759daa82c214a10a4a38ff4972d3e85","tid":544574,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34f8805f1c3c21c7aa51a250835f0c498b1cc292","tid":544574,"uid":128565,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"沖開液態氮<im